WEBVTT

00:02.068 --> 00:04.888
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:09.893 --> 00:11.895
(tape rewinding)

00:11.895 --> 00:13.396
(beeping)

00:13.396 --> 00:14.898
Hi, Sam, this is Carla.

00:14.898 --> 00:16.900
I'll be in a little late today.

00:16.900 --> 00:19.402
Eddie's really down
about his losing streak,

00:19.903 --> 00:21.404
and I want to cheer him up.

00:21.404 --> 00:23.406
It may take six or seven hours.

00:23.406 --> 00:25.408
You know hockey players. Bye.

00:25.408 --> 00:26.409
(beeping)

00:26.409 --> 00:28.411
DIANE: Hi, Sam, it's me.

00:28.411 --> 00:31.414
I'm on a little break from the trial.

00:31.414 --> 00:35.418
We had some of the most
fascinating testimony today.

00:35.418 --> 00:38.421
Of course, I'm not at
liberty to discuss it.

00:38.421 --> 00:40.924
Suffice it to say...

00:40.924 --> 00:44.544
(tape fast-forwarding)

00:44.544 --> 00:48.548
...and the defendant had the
unmitigated gall to get...

00:48.548 --> 00:51.017
Oh, uh, they're calling us back in.

00:51.017 --> 00:53.019
I have to go. Love you. Bye.

00:53.019 --> 00:54.521
(beeping)

00:55.021 --> 00:55.822
Uh, this is Woody.

00:56.022 --> 00:57.524
Sam, uh, I got home tonight

00:57.524 --> 00:59.526
and remembered Diane
called after you left

00:59.526 --> 01:01.528
and wanted me to give you a message.

01:01.528 --> 01:04.280
I love you. Bye.

01:04.280 --> 01:06.699
(beeping)

01:06.699 --> 01:08.234
Uh, Sam, this is Woody again.

01:08.234 --> 01:10.236
That message
I just left--

01:10.236 --> 01:13.156
you understand it was Diane
saying I love you, not me.

01:13.156 --> 01:15.125
All right, bye.

01:15.125 --> 01:16.626
(beeping)

01:16.626 --> 01:18.628
This is Woody again.

01:18.628 --> 01:22.332
Uh, don't misunderstand
me, I really like you a lot.

01:24.751 --> 01:26.136
(beeping)

01:26.136 --> 01:27.554
This is Woody again.

01:27.554 --> 01:30.390
Uh, I've been thinking it over, Sam.

01:30.390 --> 01:32.809
I do love you.

